Unitron/Koga Shuko/Serpentor/Anubis/Hades:





Koga Shuko looked to Unitron, who had the crate filled to the brim, lid shut.

"Excellent.  Deliver this to the Maximals...at the Ark."

"As you command, Koga Shuko." Unitron said, motioning for Hades and Anubis to 
follow him, all three robots heading for the outside of the Newcomer base.

---

Serpentor slipped into the Newcomer base, hopping into a CR chamber.
